{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ARIA techniques","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O ARIA define as semânticas que podem ser aplicadas aos elementos, e são divididas em <strong>funções</strong> (definindo um tipo de elemento da interface do usuário) e <strong>estados</strong> e <strong>propriedades</strong> que são suportados por uma função. Os autores devem atribuir uma função ARIA e os estados e propriedades apropriados a um elemento durante seu ciclo de vida, a menos que o elemento já possua semântica ARIA apropriada (através do uso de um elemento HTML apropriado). A adição de semântica ARIA apenas expõe informações extras para a API de acessibilidade de um navegador e não afeta o DOM de uma página.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções","title":"Funções","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_widget","title":"Funções de widget","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/button_role\" title=\"Using the button role\">button</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/checkbox_role\" title=\"Using the checkbox role\">checkbox</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\">gridcell</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_link_role\" title=\"Using the Link role\">link</a></li>\n <li>menuitem</li>\n <li>menuitemcheckbox&nbsp;</li>\n <li>menuitemradio</li>\n <li>option</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_progressbar_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_progressbar_role\">progressbar</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\">radio</a></li>\n <li>scrollbar</li>\n <li>searchbox</li>\n <li>separator (when focusable)</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_slider_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_slider_role\">slider</a></li>\n <li>spinbutton</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/switch_role\">switch</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\">tab</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\">tabpanel</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_textbox_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_textbox_role\">textbox</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/treeitem_role\">treeitem</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_compostas","title":"Funções compostas","isH3":true,"content":"<p>As técnicas abaixo descrevem cada função composta, bem como suas funções filho obrigatórias e opcionais.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>combobox</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/grid_role\">grid</a>&nbsp;(incluindo as funções&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\">row</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\">gridcell</a>, rowheader, columnheader)</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_listbox_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_listbox_role\">listbox</a>&nbsp;(incluindo a&nbsp;função&nbsp;option)</li>\n <li>menu</li>\n <li>menubar</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\">radiogroup (veja a função&nbsp;radio)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tablist_role\">tablist</a>&nbsp;(incluindo as funções&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\">tab</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\">tabpanel</a>)</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tree_role\">tree</a></li>\n <li>treegrid</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_da_estrutura_de_documento","title":"Funções da estrutura de&nbsp;documento","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/application_role\">application</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/article_role\" title=\"en/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_article_role\">article</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/cell_role\">cell</a></li>\n <li>columnheader</li>\n <li>definition</li>\n <li>directory</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/document_role\">document</a></li>\n <li>feed</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/figure_role\">figure</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_group_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_group_role\">group</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/heading_role\">heading</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Role_Img\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">img</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/list_role\">list</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listitem_role\">listitem</a></li>\n <li>math</li>\n <li>none</li>\n <li>note</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_presentation_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_presentation_role\">presentation</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\">row</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/rowgroup_role\">rowgroup</a></li>\n <li>rowheader</li>\n <li>separator</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/table_role\">table</a></li>\n <li>term</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/textbox_role\">textbox</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_toolbar_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_toolbar_role\">toolbar</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tooltip_role\">tooltip</a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Funções da estrutura de documento"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_ponto_de_referência","title":"Funções de ponto de referência","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_banner_role\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_banner_role\">banner</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Complementary_role\">complementary</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/contentinfo_role\">contentinfo</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/form_role\">form</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/main_role\">main</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/navigation_role\">navigation</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/region_role\">region</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/search_role\">search</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_regiões_ativa","title":"Funções de regiões ativa","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/alert_role\">alert</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_log_role\" title=\"Using the Log role\">log</a></li>\n <li>marquee</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_status_role\" title=\"Using the link role\">status</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/timer_role\">timer</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_janela","title":"Funções de janela","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/alertdialog_role\">alertdialog</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/dialog_role\">dialog</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"estados_e_propriedades","title":"Estados e propriedades","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_de_widget","title":"Atributos de widget","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>aria-autocomplete</li>\n <li>aria-checked</li>\n <li>aria-current</li>\n <li>aria-disabled</li>\n <li>aria-errormessage</li>\n <li>aria-expanded</li>\n <li>aria-haspopup</li>\n <li>aria-hidden</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-invalid_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-invalid attribute\">aria-invalid</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-label_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-labelledby attribute\">aria-label</a></li>\n <li>aria-level</li>\n <li>aria-modal</li>\n <li>aria-multiline</li>\n <li>aria-multiselectable</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-orientation_attribute\" title=\"en/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-orientation_attribute\">aria-orientation</a></li>\n <li>aria-placeholder</li>\n <li>aria-pressed</li>\n <li>aria-readonly</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-required_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-required property\">aria-required</a></li>\n <li>aria-selected</li>\n <li>aria-sort</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemax_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-required attribute\">aria-valuemax</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute\" title=\"en/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuemin_attribute\">aria-valuemin</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuenow_attribute\" title=\"en/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuenow_attribute\">aria-valuenow</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuetext_attribute\" title=\"en/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-valuetext_attribute\">aria-valuetext</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_da_região_ativa","title":"Atributos da região ativa","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>aria-live</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-relevant_attribute\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">aria-relevant</a></li>\n <li>aria-atomic</li>\n <li>aria-busy</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_de_drag_drop","title":"Atributos de drag &amp; drop","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>aria-dropeffect</li>\n <li>aria-dragged</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Atributos de drag & drop"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos_de_relacionamento","title":"Atributos de relacionamento","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-activedescendant_attribute\" title=\"Role\">aria-activedescendant</a></li>\n <li>aria-colcount</li>\n <li>aria-colindex</li>\n <li>aria-colspan</li>\n <li>aria-controls</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-describedby_attribute\" title=\"Using the aria-labelledby attribute\">aria-describedby</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Annotations#associating_annotated_elements_with_their_details\">aria-details</a></li>\n <li>aria-errormessage</li>\n <li>aria-flowto</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-labelledby_attribute\" title=\"en/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-labelledby_attribute\">aria-labelledby</a></li>\n <li>aria-owns</li>\n <li>aria-posinset</li>\n <li>aria-rowcount</li>\n <li>aria-rowindex</li>\n <li>aria-rowspan</li>\n <li>aria-setsize</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades_específicas_do_microsoftedge","title":"Propriedades específicas do MicrosoftEdge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/x-ms-aria-flowfrom\">x-ms-aria-flowfrom</a>&nbsp;<svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Funções","id":"funções"},{"text":"Estados e propriedades","id":"estados_e_propriedades"}],"summary":"O ARIA define as semânticas que podem ser aplicadas aos elementos, e são divididas em funções (definindo um tipo de elemento da interface do usuário) e estados e propriedades que são suportados por uma função. Os autores devem atribuir uma função ARIA e os estados e propriedades apropriados a um elemento durante seu ciclo de vida, a menos que o elemento já possua semântica ARIA apropriada (através do uso de um elemento HTML apropriado). A adição de semântica ARIA apenas expõe informações extras para a API de acessibilidade de um navegador e não afeta o DOM de uma página.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ARIA Techniken","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Using ARIA: Roles, states, and properties","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ARIA techniques","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Techniques ARIA","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ARIA を使用する: ロール、ステート、プロパティ","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"ARIA 사용하기: 규칙, 상태, 속성","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Использование ARIA","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"使用 ARIA：角色、状态和属性","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Using ARIA","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques/index.html","last_commit_